                    <span>Truly useful how-to-secure your server book. Goes through locking down your OS, web server (IIS), SQL Server installation,<BR>.NET configuration, and web application do's and don'ts.<BR>Very helpful when I configured a server which I rented from a dedicated machine hosting service.<BR>Only reason for four stars rather than five, it is really based around Windows 2000 server. Needs to be updated for Windows 2003 server.</span>
                  
              
